net.opentsdb.core

类 IncomingDataPoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.opentsdb.core.IncomingDataPoint
  • 直接已知子类:
    HistogramPojo, RollUpDataPoint

    public class IncomingDataPoint
extends Object
    Bridging class that stores a normalized data point parsed from the "put" RPC methods and gets it ready for storage. Also has some helper methods that were formerly in the Tags class for parsing values.

    The data point value is a string in order to accept a wide range of values including floating point and scientific. Before storage, the value will be parsed to the appropriate numeric type.

    Note the class is not marked as final since some serializers may want to overload with their own fields or parsing methods.

    从以下版本开始:
    2.0
